Open android studio.
Go to the folder named as drawable under the res directory.
Copy the images in the images folder into the drawable folder.
Create a new folder and rename it as raw under the res directory.
Copy the song you want to play into the raw folder.
Copy the code from activity_main.txt file into the activity_main.xml file. 
Copy the code from Mainactivity.txt file into the MainActivity.java file.
Connect your android device and click on build.
If android device is not available then download android virtual device and then build using the virtual device.
The apk will installed and launched automatically in your android device.
